    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler Virt SIG 是什么？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler Virt SIG（Special Interest Group，特别兴趣小组）负责 The virt team is responsible for exploration of the virtualization and cloud native runtime technology.。该 SIG 共有 37 名核心成员，维护 28 个代码仓库，属于 虚拟化 领域。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "如何参与 openEuler Virt SIG？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "参与 openEuler Virt SIG 的方式：1）向相关仓库（如 openeuler/skylark、openeuler/vmtop、src-openeuler/libvirt-glib）提交 Pull Request；2）订阅邮件列表 virt@openeuler.org；3）参加 SIG 定期工作会议，会议信息见 openEuler 官网活动日历。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler Virt SIG 包含哪些代码仓库？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler Virt SIG 共维护 28 个代码仓库，主要包括：openeuler/skylark、openeuler/vmtop、src-openeuler/libvirt-glib 等。完整列表见 https://www.openeuler.org/zh/sig/Virt。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler Virt SIG 的 Maintainer 是谁？",
